message.body: Hi turklin!
Are you still in sleepsville
Congratulations on winning the raffle
Hello!
I'm sorry I'm at work.
How did u know I won the raffle?
Text penn news said so
But I know you. Don't say my name but I'm the person that told you about the study.
How was u r NYC show?
Hey!!!
Heehee
It's Wednesday
How is your day going
I wish I was sleepsville
I mean my show is Thursday
I'm going to ny tonight to prepare
I got business cards
Where are you working these days?
And stickers and I'm showing my interactive pieces
I just updated my website
Wanna look it over with a critical eye?
Or just a fun one?
Or a lazy one
Oh hey
Are you done with school
Well good luck with the show. Are you showing your small landscapes?
My day is going ok despite the rain
This is just super xciting for me
Yes but also other stuff!!!!
You want me to look over the work? I can look at it if you want.
What is the interactive work that you mentioned?
And two new pieces not for sale.
Oh dear. It's not raining here.
Monday. Blues?
Sure!!!
Do you have fancy clothes picked out for the opening?
The interactive piece is called the mobile music box
What are you working on???
You always look so beautiful.
Should I look on ur website.
Oh I saw met Matt neff Ivanco and Marc recently.
Marc& Giana are no more;(
But Marc is dating Anna neighbor. It's awesome.
I'm doing paperwork so it's easy for me to text now.
Before I was labor.
That is a very nice complement. I don't always feel beautiful.
I do have clothes picked out!!! How did u know?
Clothes and shoes
The music box sounds fun. How does it work?
I don't have a website.
Sorry I'm getting your texts all out of order.
!!u always look handsome too!!
Hand me some, handsome!
Y not.
Photocells and pd patch
U don't have to apologize
I sent a lot
Y don't u have a site
You are very beautiful inside and out even if you don't always feel that way. You helped me feel better remember?
I just don't want to spend my time on a site. I rather be doing anything. I'm not into self promotion.
I'll check out your site for sure though!
U helped me feel better. But just bc I helped u doesn't make me beautiful. Haha. That was a long time ago. It does however make us friends I guess. Wehelped each other thru a hard time.
I guess u don't remember when I was mean to you.
Haha
I hate self promotion. It's another job. But I'm doing it now.
Bc I'm desperate for something bigger.
You were never mean to me!
You should be going after something bigger because you deserve it.
I wish I could go to the opening.
I was terrible to you. I just stopped talking to u. After I found out about Elana. I would never treat anyone like that now. I still feel Bad.
It would be awesome if U came to the show. !!!!!
Omg!
U should come.
U should come to boston and come to the beach
I wanna go to the beach so bad
All the time
I would love to go to the beach. I think this summer will be real busy for me but I love going to the beach.
The last time I went I swam with dolphins
Do u have any fun summer adventures planned
But that was in sea isle city, not Boston
I have some art stuff in the works but I have to fly to minnisota to get a root canal in July.
It's a long story but the dentist said he would do it for free if I went out there.
And I had frequent flyer miles to cover it
I had forgotten you got mad at me. I just like to remember the good times I guess.
I miss having you around to cheer me up though
Oh no why did I remind you?
Haha. I love cheering up Nice ppl
Life is hard so sometimes we forget how fun hard can be.
You still do cheer me up I guess when you send me pics of beautiful flowers
You are a very warm person and have a good outlook on life
Oh yes!!! I always think of you when I see flowers.
Well only the really pretty ones.
Pretty/colorful/cool/exotic
I'm a cuddler!
I'm glad you are still painting and having a good life
I know, it is infectious
How long do you have left in school? Are you done?
I wish that wast job. Training puppies to cuddle.
I would just take naps with the cutest puppies ever
I am not painting at the moment.
I am self promoting.
I have another year of school left. Life is really nice here but I still miss my friends in Philly. I get lonely sometimes.
Mostly though I try to find momentum in terms if a career as a media researcher whatever that means.
I think I need to get involved at MIT
But I don't feel smart enough.
Thought I Know that's stupid.
Bc I feel like I have an opinion to offer.
You are totally smart enough to be at mit but if not Are you going to come back to Philly when your done with school?!
Thought I Know that's stupid.
I dunno.
I want to work. I'd like that. Maybe I can teach at penn someday
Teaching at penn would be be the best. I mean if ivancho can do it...
Eeeee
Haha
I have a question?
How did u come up with the name web foot?
And are u at work?
And how did u know this was me?
Did u just guess?
Also do u want to send me pictures of your work?
Webfoot because I like dark wing duck.
I am at work right now
I knew it was u because you sent me an email when you won and then it was posted on the textpenn site
I do want to send you pictures of my work!
I have been working on collaborative sculpture lately and applying for some shows.
Oh sorry i went to the doctor and when I came back we were back to manual labor. Ill text u more around five?
If not sooner... Do u stop at five?
Are you texting on a computer
I'm texting on an iPhone
Sure whenever u can!
I'm on an iPhone too
Hope you are ok
No way!!!!!
Way
I'm ok. Just a regular check up. I have super low blood pressure.
I have super high blood pressure, if we could share our blood we could both have perfect blood pressure!
Perfect blood pressure that's insanity!
So are u paid to text me???
And also how does the raffle work? Am I an amazing texter?
Or do a lot of people win?
I text just for fun. I don't profit.
You are just a lucky one!
Whoa! Ah so cool.
I tried to get so many people to do it with me.
No one wanted too
Did hunter win?
Hunter didn't do it , I don't think he has unlimited text
Oh you aren't on family plan with him?
No but that's a good idea
Does hunter want an iPhone?
How is hunter
I just ate Chinese food for dinner. So good
What are you having?
He's good he has his own construction business and an old iPhone
Chinese sounds really good I had leftover burritos
Really what kind of construction
Mostly rehab stuff, porches, floors, windows plumbing electric kitchens and baths
You help too
Oh man we never talked about the old porn theater collapsing
I help out once and a while when he has too much work
Your nice
Did you see the damage done by the collapsing city
Where u ok? People u know ok?
I didn't mean to be insensitive
I'm fine I didn't know anyone involved in the collapse but I did walk past the building twice the day before it fell
Were u scared?
No I wasn't scared. A demolition crew did the same thing in west Philly destroying 2 buildings but no one was killed.
I think it is developers paying demo crews to destroy buildings that lower property values but that is just conjecture
Hmm maybe. Some guy turned himself in right?
Does insurance pay out when that happens?
I have no idea
Well. People. In your city are corrupt!
And criminal. Boston people are nerdy
I thought that Boston was totally corrupt! What about the big dig?
Oh my! I know the answer: the world is corrupt!!!!
The world people aren't honest ;(
I'm On the train to ny
Now!
It's comfortable but I forgot my headphones and I want to listen to radiolab. Very upsetting.
Oh boy good luck with the show. How long is the train ride from Boston
A few hours. Don't worry I won't text u the whole time?
You can text me as much as you can! I love it
Texting with you is great
Haha.
That's nice
I'm excited to see my parents
Not funny it's true
My dad built a tricopter drone thing
And my mom is momsanity
How is your family
Do you still have to install anything or is it set up already ?
No I'm going to install tomorrow
But I'm Not allowed to put holes in the wall
I don't get a long great with my family but they are ok. We didn't talk for a couple of years but we are talking a little now
It's not really a show
It's more like an art market
It's nice that your parents seem so great
How can you hang stuff with out holes?
Tape?
Velcro?
Yeah. But sometimes I think I'm too close with them.
Iike maybe ill never have a family of my own :(
I'm building some portable stands in my dads basement
Why not? Do you not want a family?
Very ghetto
But one night only
(Since I'm Not handy - it's just: plywood to lean against the walls
No I really want a family!
I am so baby fever
It's so typical
I want children
People will be looking at the art and won't care about the wall behind it
It will be great
I want someone to raise them with me but I'm afraid ill never find anyone. So Ingrid and her boyfriend said they would help.
I want a career and puppies and babies!!!
I can help!
Oh man I hope so.
You would be a great mom
Everyone wants puppies
I want cuddles and financial assistance from a devoted partner
When do you want to have these babys?
I want a studio
Where I can paint
And have lots of light
Do u want puppies?
I just want so many things!
But most importantly I want to write a book Someday - or the visual Equivalent.
Of course I want puppies I am a dog person
You have to get all that stuff one at a time though
I hate cats!!!
Shhhh
I want to have babies in the next five years
Yeah
I live with a cat. Cats are fine but they aren't as great as dogs
Well I'm working on trying to learn how to get things that I want.
I'm planting seeds for research while getting my masters
Do you want a dog sometime?
Yes I want a big dog! Which means ill need a bigger place to live first
Hunters house isn't big enough?
What are u doing now? Are you sure this isn't too much texting? Can u win The raffle?
No cuz most of it is not mine.
Don't worry it's fun!
Just stop if you get tired. I'll do the same
Ok.
Agreed.
Text shake.
What kind of things do you want in the next few years?
Text shake
A house and a dog and a better gallery. Then kiddos.
Someone to be supportive and cheer me up is important to
How many kiddos ?
It's so much easier for men. Ingrid keeps telling me I have to start looking for potential baby daddy's now! Because I only have a few years left.
One or two tikes
You have a long time don't rush it.
You will be happy
You sound so confident over text messages
Do you want a bunch of tiny ones?
I am confident
Well I want to have at least one of my own.
I want to be a fat sweaty pregnant lady
Ha
I just really want to be pregnant.
To see what it's like
Maybe that's weird
After that, who knows? Maybe ill adopt or foster if I'm lucky enough to afford more than one
I think I'd be a good mom too
I'd be a little overbearing but I think I'd have the confidence that my children will tough.
I'd respect them
You would look real cute with a baby bump
You are such a loving person you will be the best mom
Did I tell You ? I got in my first bar fight! It was only verbal (not physical) but I stood up to a very nasty man !!!!
That's good that you stood up for your self but you could get hurt. What did he do to you?
No. I was with a lot of people. He's in my program. He told me I was annoying and hated me and then tried to drink my beer. He was egging me on
So I stood on my bar stool and said: I've hit manlier men than you before. You soft balding fat asshole!
And walked away.
He was belittling me
I don't think I'd look Good pregnant but I think it would be fun.
I would pretend to have cravings for things I didn't really have cravings for and make people but me ice Cream and blueberries and anchovy pizza.
You will look great pregnant! You will also have cravings for weird things you never even thought of craving before.
And some things will make you sick just from the smell
It will be a crazy journey
Cool. Do you want to be pregnant?
I just tested my music box on the Amtrak!
You will be an excellent mom because you are an excellent lady
Ha
I want to be with someone who is pregnant some day
How does the music box work
You will be an excellent dad too! You will run around a big house with your tikes and big dog. And you will all have lemonade when you are hot and sweaty.
Except the pooch
He'll only have water.
It uses an arduino and light sensors.
And I had help writing a bunch of code to allow the data from the light sensors to manipulate the code.
What is an arduino?
Sounds pretty cool
A little computer thing
Google it!
It's hi tech!
I'm in new haven.
I used to spend a lot of time there
I had a boyfriend at Yale while I was in college

I'm not.
I'm learning
I'm trying
It's really hard
That's mine.
Oh no I just sent U a picture
Will u get it
You are a smart little flower
No I'm an over thinker I'm very critical
I like to ask questions
Answers and solutions and knowing doesn't sit right with me
No I can't see pictures. U have to text it to my regular number
That is being smart!
You know that
Hee her
I'm Arrogant enough
I'm so happy we are having this conversation.
It's fun. I really hope everything is going well With you.
And that everything you want you will get. But u know all that already.
You are a firecracker
I glad too!
Haha
I love being called a firecracker.
Cool
What are you?
What's your secret power?
Some things are good and some are bad but I'm still trying to keep myself and others happy
You will be success full and happy too
I don't have a secret power, you just bring out the best in me

You see good in people mister.
Oh I'm the emotion keeper - I cry on command
Yeah you are a real pure soul
Don't go getting jaded in New York
I'm gona hit the hey soon it was great to text with you. Good luck with the show!
Talk to you soon!!! Thanks for a great train ride b
Text me in real life if you wana talk anytime
Hope to see you some time
Same goes. Yes!!!!
You are the best
Good Night firefly
